org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl

Class FigureImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • EObjectImpl
      • org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl.FigureImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Figure, Primitive
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChartViewImpl, FigureContainerImpl, ImageImpl, ShapeImpl, TextImpl

    public abstract class FigureImpl
extends EObjectImpl
implements Figure
    An implementation of the model object 'Figure'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Name
    • Foreground Color
    • Background Color
    • Size
    • On Click
    • On Double Click
    • Cursor
    • Visible
    • Border
    • Opaque
    • Tool Tip
